section.section.map-sct
	.map-sct__infobox.col-lg-8.col-md-20.col-sm-20.col-xs-20
		.map-sct__content
			h3.map-sct__title.uppercase
				|Наш адрес
			table.col-md-10
				tr
					td(rowspan=2).map-sct__address
						i(class="fa fa-map-marker", aria-hidden="true").map-sct__icon
						.map-sct__text
							| 115554
							br
							| Отличный город,
							br
							| Первая улица, дом 22

					td.map-sct__link.map-sct__telephone
						i(class="fa fa-phone", aria-hidden="true").map-sct__icon
						| +7 987 654 32 11
				tr
					td
						a.map-sct__link.map-sct__email(href="mailto:info@economenergo.ru")
							i(class="fa fa-envelope-open", aria-hidden="true").map-sct__icon.map-sct__icon_mail
							| info@economenergo.ru

			.map-sct__pic.col-lg-20.col-md-10.col-sm-10.col-xs-10
				img(src="img/content/office.jpg", alt="Building photo")

